 Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n			+ Lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; những biện ph&aacute;p xử l&yacute; hữu hiệu v&agrave; th&ocirc;ng minh khi sơn tường cũ, nh&agrave; cũ.</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; font-size: 13px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n			+ Lựa chọn m&agrave;u sắc tinh tế, s&aacute;ng tạo</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; font-size: 13px; border: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n			+ Ti&ecirc;u ch&iacute;&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; border: none; text-decoration: underline; background: transparent;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; border: none; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; border: none; text-decoration: none; background: transparent;"><a href="http://sonnha.dep.asia/dich-vu-son-nha/son-nha-cu/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; border: none; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(51, 102, 153); background: transparent;" title="sơn